<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">周颂·时迈</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contson316a0e7b64b1">
<p>时迈其邦，昊天其子之，实右序有周。薄言震之，莫不震叠。怀柔百神，及河乔岳，允王维后。</p>
<p>明昭有周，式序在位。载戢干戈，载橐弓矢。我求懿德，肆于时夏，允王保之。</p>
</div>
</div>
